snippet.title: FailRace
snippet.description:
FailRace is a place where cars are raced, rolled, put through incredible challenges and sometimes crashed rather spectacularly all for your entertainment on some of the best driving video games around.

If you are feeling super generous you can help support this channel on patreon :), the link can be found below
